WEBVTT

00:06:59.331 --> 00:07:01.967
I have lived all of my life

00:07:01.991 --> 00:07:06.038
next door to a man
who continuously beats up his wife.

00:07:07.506 --> 00:07:09.045
Two weeks ago,

00:07:09.069 --> 00:07:11.776
I was listening to my radio,

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:14.212
and your voice came on,

00:07:14.236 --> 00:07:18.756
and you spoke about something
called the HeForShe,

00:07:18.780 --> 00:07:21.660
and the need for men to play their role.

00:07:23.023 --> 00:07:28.705
Within a few hours, I heard
the woman cry again next door,

00:07:28.729 --> 00:07:31.149
but for the first time,